Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: python-ucto
Version: 0.2.1
Summary: This is a Python binding to the tokenizer Ucto. Tokenisation is one of the first step in almost any Natural Language Processing task, yet it is not always as trivial a task as it appears to be. This binding makes the power of the ucto tokeniser available to Python. Ucto itself is a regular-expression based, extensible, and advanced tokeniser written in C++ (http://ilk.uvt.nl/ucto).
Home-page: http://github.com/proycon/python-ucto
Author: Maarten van Gompel
Author-email: proycon@anaproy.nl
License: GPL
